school_name: International Academy of Design and Technology
comments: This school recently became Sanford Brown, changing its name from IADT. Katina is a good instructor, and I learned a ton in her class. She is helpful, and willing to work with students who need more attention. I would definitely take it and recommend it. A lot of material is covered in a short amount of time, I wish I could review it again.

school_name: International Academy of Design and Technology
comments: Outstanding! Very informative and fun! Lots of creative options and learned alot!
